rows.label: qst202019_msg0001
rows.name: Oh, hello again. How is it going?

rows.label: qst202019_msg0002
rows.name:
Here are the ingredients I'd like you
to find:

rows.label: qst202019_msg0003
rows.name:
5 clumps of Salty Soil, 8 portions
of Gromrice, and 5 Ruby Mangosteens.

rows.label: qst202019_msg0101
rows.name:
Why, thank you! This is everything,
isn't it?

rows.label: qst202019_msg0102
rows.name:
It must have taken you quite some
time.

rows.label: qst202019_msg0104
rows.name:
Could I perhaps invite you round for
dinner? Really it's the least I could do.

rows.label: qst202019_msg0108
rows.name:
My house is on the far side of Tretl
Windmill Plaza. Do come!
